            WriteLiteral(@"</h1>

<h3>Morto Sweepstakes - Fifa World Cup 2022 Rules</h3>

<h4>HOW TO ENTER:</h4>
<p>If you are eligible to participe on the sweepstake game you will receive a link so you can register. You must be over 18 years old. After registering you will receive a confirmation e-mail so you can login and place your bets.</p>

<h4>SWEEPSTAKES PERIOD:</h4>
<p>You should always check our website to check if the bets are available. As soon as Fifa makes the draw of the groups and release the game dates and matches, we will make the bets available. You should place the bets at any time before a game starts. After a game starts you won't be able to place or edit your bets.</p>

<h4>GAME FEE:</h4>
<p>Before receiving your confirmation e-mail you need to deposit the entry fee of CAD 50.</p>

<h4>POINTS:</h4>
<h5>Regular points</h5>
<ol>
    <li>Exact match results, winner and score: 20 points</li>
    <li>Right winner and score from only one team: 13 points</li>
    <li>Right winner and the score differenc");
