    <li>Right winner, wrong score but right score difference: 10 points</li>
    <li>Wrong winner but right score for one of the teams: 3 points</li>
</ol>
<h5>Extra points for top 4 teams</h5>
<ol>
    <li>If you guess the 4th place: 30 points</li>
    <li>If you guess the 3rd place: 40 points</li>
    <li>If you guess the 2nd place: 70 points</li>
    <li>If you guess the 1st place: 120 points</li>
</ol>

<h4>WINNERS:</h4>
<p>The top 3 players with most points will receive a prize:</p>
<ol>
    <li>1st: 70% of the total value paid by all participants.</li>
    <li>2nd: 20% of the total value paid by all participants</li>
